{"tid":1343656,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[對抗驚黑合作] 公民拘捕權","createTime":"2019-07-21T19:10:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T19:48:43.000Z","uid":199145,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"83bdc40da65e850500fae19045ee54a9e3dbc57d","tid":1343656,"uid":199145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:10:06.000Z","msg":"如果你遇到暴徒（包括並不限於元朗暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）你可以選擇根據刑事罪行條例第101條拘捕佢，並於reasonable time內移送驚賊/<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">裁判官席前</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSECTION 221 Criminal Ordinance - 101<br />\n(5)Every person who arrests any person under any of the provisions herein contained shall (if the person making the arrest is not himself a police officer) deliver the person so arrested, and the property, if any, taken possession of by him, to some police officer in order that he may be conveyed as soon as reasonably may be before a magistrate, to be by him dealt with according to law, or <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">himself convey him before a magistrate, as soon as reasonably may be, for that purpose. </span></span></strong>(Amended 51 of 1911; 2 of 1912 Schedule)"},{"pid":"011c53dc3ea3ab4f0fb541c39787057324bcb60a","tid":1343656,"uid":199145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9dd5b46e962cfb81b68efe476a9af985a3d13d","tid":1343656,"uid":199145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a6d89ffd6d843a76fa526ffce0e46cc8405d3d","tid":1343656,"uid":199145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"